@DATABASE "Black Tiger"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Black Tiger"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                                Black Tiger
                                ===========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46065,0)"}         46065,0
@{"Energy = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(45661,255)"}         45661,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(44939,0)"}         44939,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
